## Usage

### Run Marimo Notebook

```bash
# Edit mode (interactive)
uv run marimo edit notebooks/example.py

# Run mode (read-only)
uv run marimo run notebooks/example.py
```

### Create New Notebook

```bash
uv run marimo edit notebooks/new_notebook.py
```

